title: Brand New 2 Bedroom 2 Bath!! Modern Mfd Space #81

posting_body: Are you looking for a place to call home?
Our community is on the El Camino walking distance to shopping, great restaurants, and a park.
Our community offers a clubhouse, pool, laundry facilities, workout area, billiard room, and car wash.
We have a friendly and professional staff ready to welcome you to your new place.
The greatest price in Sunnyvale is at Rancho La Mesa.
Rancho La Mesa Mobile Home Community is happy to announce our 2 bedrooms/ 1 bathroom home is for rent.
This home features modern appliances, including a dishwasher, and microwave, as well as central heating and air conditioning.
It also has a washer and dryer.
This energy-star-rated home is the perfect blend of modern and comfortable.
Please see below what your home features.
- stainless steel sink with the garbage disposal
Close to El Camino / Lawrence Exp.
- please provide documents to show the ability to pay rent.
